@startuml
title Phased Delivery Dependency Map

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 10
}

rectangle "Phase 1\nHardening and release confidence" as P1
rectangle "Phase 2\nCompany and storage scope" as P2
rectangle "Phase 3\nStock movement truth" as P3
rectangle "Phase 4\nDocuments and job pipelines" as P4
rectangle "Phase 5\nInstallable product and domain profiles" as P5

P1 --> P2
P2 --> P3
P3 --> P4
P1 --> P5
P4 --> P5

note right of P3
Do not implement rich document automation
before ownership and stock semantics are stable.
end note

note right of P5
Autoparts-specific profile work belongs here,
after generic catalog and document foundations exist.
end note
@enduml
